trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo" /> 物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> class allows you to programmatically access and modify tag-prefix information stored in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>類別可讓您以程式設計方式存取及修改儲存在組態檔中的標記前置詞資訊。

trans-unit.source: Tag prefixes associate a "namespace" in ASP.NET with the assemblies and namespaces that must be included for custom controls and user controls to work properly.
trans-unit.target: 標記前置詞會在 ASP.NET 中的"namespace"關聯的組件和命名空間必須包含自訂控制項和使用者控制項才能正常運作。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> objects are stored as members of a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> 物件會儲存為成員<xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection>物件。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection> class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `controls` subsection of the `pages` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection>類別可讓您以程式設計方式存取和修改`controls`小節的`pages`組態檔區段。

trans-unit.target: 下列組態檔摘錄示範如何以宣告方式指定的數個屬性的值<xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection>型別。

trans-unit.target: 它會呼叫 ASP.NET 組態系統。

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection>類別一定會包含執行個體<xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection>型別。

trans-unit.source: Use this instance, rather than creating your own.
trans-unit.target: 這個執行個體，而不是建立您自己使用。

trans-unit.source: If it does, a <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationException> will be thrown.
